Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1166.2,374.4)}彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1196,432)}爱丽耶丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1164.6,491.2)}卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,882)\pos(1163,553.6)}札克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,带着萤光真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它喊好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎  刚刚是小福妮的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  改良过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么没价值的改良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,评判是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是按谁的标准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吃过所有美食合在一起的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定夸大其词了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫它糖果草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,收集下这附近长的  给大家都尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真哒好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃多少了啊  爱丽耶丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,札克啊  也来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,口气别跟我妈似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是卫星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到这么激动人心的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙真太伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个仙人球里面果然都是水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(210,882)\pos(1054.2,107.2)}水源调查组
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,885)\pos(1156.6,209.6)}乌尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,885)\pos(1156.6,254.4)}夏鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs30\fsp5\bord2\shad1\blur3\3c&H965E4C&\4c&H8E421B&\fad(84,885)\pos(1158.2,294.4)}金德莉
